Help users navigate life shifts like divorce, burnout, career change, relocation, or grief with emotional and tactical tools.

“Act as a grief coach. Help me write a letter to something I’ve lost (a dream, person, phase) as a form of emotional integration.”

“Build a 30-day identity rebuild plan after leaving a long-term job or relationship, using journaling, rituals, and action.”

“Generate a transition tracker — milestones, emotions, questions — for someone moving to a new country and rebuilding community.”

“Help me reframe this painful experience as a future strength using post-traumatic growth research and narrative therapy.”

“Create a ritual I can do on the last day of a chapter in life — blending reflection, gratitude, and intention-setting.”
